Hindi ka ba nag-e-enjoy na naka-confine?

00:13:09.550 --> 00:13:10.750
I-lock si Wang Heng.

00:13:11.150 --> 00:13:12.630
Liu He, nawala ka na ba sa isip mo?

00:13:13.200 --> 00:13:14.040
Panginoon Gong.

00:13:14.750 --> 00:13:15.790
Panginoon Gong.

00:13:21.360 --> 00:13:22.750
Zhao Han, Wang Wen.

00:13:24.270 --> 00:13:25.910
Li Chuang, Wu Jun.

00:13:26.390 --> 00:13:27.240
Pumasok ka sa loob.

00:13:27.670 --> 00:13:30.270
Li Ye, Liu Yudong, Wei Ping.

00:13:30.630 --> 00:13:32.150
Yin Xiangwen, Zhang Qian.

00:13:32.600 --> 00:13:33.440
Lin Yuankai.

00:13:33.570 --> 00:13:34.420
Qian Hongxin.

00:13:34.510 --> 00:13:36.070
Ang limampung ito ay babalik sa Changyi.

00:13:36.720 --> 00:13:37.760
Ang natitirang dalawang daan,

00:13:38.120 --> 00:13:39.200
sundan mo ako.

00:13:39.390 --> 00:13:40.590
Aalis na kami

00:13:40.960 --> 00:13:42.300
para sa Chang'an sabay-sabay.

00:13:42.590 --> 00:13:44.830
Mahusay!

00:13:51.180 --> 00:13:57.340
(Longshan Inn, Dingtao, Changyi)

00:13:57.340 --> 00:13:58.460
(Jiyang)

00:13:58.620 --> 00:14:00.500
(Jiyang)

00:14:07.980 --> 00:14:09.660
(Jiyang)

00:14:21.910 --> 00:14:22.910
Nagtatampo ka pa ba?

00:14:28.840 --> 00:14:30.840
Hindi ako kasing liit mo.

00:14:31.510 --> 00:14:32.390
Hindi ako nagtatanim ng sama ng loob.

00:14:34.000 --> 00:14:35.160
Halika, buksan mo ang pinto.

00:14:41.200 --> 00:14:42.040
Hey.

00:14:44.670 --> 00:14:45.510
Heng.

00:14:45.980 --> 00:14:48.210
Huwag mong sabihing nasasanay ka
na sa kariton ng kulungan na ito.

00:14:48.300 --> 00:14:50.230
Nagbibigay ba ito sa iyo ng labis na kagalakan?

00:14:51.210 --> 00:14:52.950
Kinulong lang kita saglit.

00:14:53.480 --> 00:14:54.390
Halos hindi big deal.

00:14:54.390 --> 00:14:55.600
Alam mo kung ano ang ibig kong sabihin.

00:15:01.160 --> 00:15:03.920
Pinamunuan ko ang aking 200 kapatid na magbahagi
ng kayamanan at kaluwalhatian.

00:15:04.510 --> 00:15:05.510
Bakit hindi ako magiging masaya?

00:15:06.920 --> 00:15:07.870
Masaya?

00:15:08.480 --> 00:15:09.320
yun ba?

00:15:10.270 --> 00:15:11.870
Wala nang hihigit pang kagalakan kaysa dito.

00:15:12.170 --> 00:15:14.420
Ngunit ang iyong higit na kagalakan ay magdudulot ng pinsala
sa marami pang buhay.

00:15:14.440 --> 00:15:15.280
Wang Heng.

00:15:15.480 --> 00:15:17.670
Gusto mo lang itaboy ang mga tauhan ko

00:15:17.670 --> 00:15:18.870
para makapag-charge ka nang mag-isa

00:15:18.870 --> 00:15:19.710
at angkinin ang Qilin?

00:15:19.720 --> 00:15:20.750
Kung lahat ng lalaki mo

00:15:21.080 --> 00:15:22.630
mamatay sa Chang'an,

00:15:23.080 --> 00:15:24.180
matutuwa ka pa ba?

00:15:29.010 --> 00:15:30.860
Nakita ko lang sa iyong plano,

00:15:31.840 --> 00:15:32.910
gayon ma'y isinumpa ninyo ang aking mga tauhan

00:15:33.480 --> 00:15:35.440
para lang sa Qilin?

00:15:36.270 --> 00:15:37.320
Makinig ka.

00:15:37.750 --> 00:15:38.840
Hindi ito sumpa.

00:15:39.030 --> 00:15:40.080
Ito ay ang Mandate of Heaven.

00:15:40.670 --> 00:15:41.600
Lahat ng mga lalaking ito ngunit ikaw

00:15:42.390 --> 00:15:43.600
gusto ng

00:15:43.760 --> 00:15:44.640
dahil sayo.

00:15:55.360 --> 00:15:56.790
Wang, sige.

00:16:01.480 --> 00:16:03.080
(Pinaalalahanan ni Chamberlain Gong
ang Duke)

00:16:03.320 --> 00:16:05.320
(at may mahigit 50 na ipinadala pabalik.)

00:16:05.430 --> 00:16:06.440
(Ang proseso ay binago,)

00:16:06.590 --> 00:16:08.010
(gayunpaman ang kinalabasan ay nanatiling pareho.)

00:16:08.510 --> 00:16:09.820
(Ang kasaysayan ay hindi nagbago sa lahat.)

00:16:29.760 --> 00:16:32.160
♪Bantayan ang bagyo;
marinig ang pagbuhos ng ulan sa gabi♪

00:16:32.160 --> 00:16:33.760
♪Hanggang sa liwanag ng bukang-liwayway♪

00:16:33.760 --> 00:16:35.480
♪Isang katotohanang hindi masabi♪

00:16:36.160 --> 00:16:37.840
♪Tama at maling bagay♪

00:16:37.840 --> 00:16:39.960
♪Gayunpaman hindi ako makakagawa ng tamang pagpipilian♪

00:16:40.160 --> 00:16:41.600
♪Ang nawalang manlalaro sa laro♪

00:16:41.840 --> 00:16:44.960
♪Gumawa ng isang liko ng kapalaran♪

00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:47.480
♪Nawala ang daan pabalik,
wala nang babalikan♪

00:16:47.480 --> 00:16:50.720
♪Hiram ang walang katapusang cycle♪

00:16:51.280 --> 00:16:54.760
♪Para ipaglaban ang pinakaperpektong resulta♪

00:16:55.520 --> 00:16:57.880
♪Paano i-trace ang mga thread
at sundin ang sanhi at epekto♪

00:16:57.880 --> 00:17:01.640
♪Naghahanap ng diskarte na walang kapintasan♪

00:17:01.920 --> 00:17:06.560
♪Paano makawala
sa nakatadhana ngunit hindi inaasahang lock na ito♪

00:17:06.720 --> 00:17:11.760
♪Upang mabuhay upang niyanig ang mundo♪

00:17:12.120 --> 00:17:16.240
♪Sa paglalakbay na ito,
nagkakaroon ako ng mas matinding kalamangan♪

00:17:16.360 --> 00:17:18.440
♪Nagplano ako
bago ako kumilos nang hindi mabilang na beses♪

00:17:18.520 --> 00:17:24.880
♪Ang nakamamatay na panganib ay naging biro♪

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:29.200
♪Sa daan na ito,
pinagmamasdan ko ang walang katapusang pagtaas-baba♪

00:17:29.240 --> 00:17:31.320
♪Nasa mga kabanata ang mga edad
ng pagkabulok at pamumulaklak♪

00:17:31.320 --> 00:17:33.240
♪Magkita tayong muli♪

00:17:33.280 --> 00:17:38.440
♪Isang nagmamadaling landas, at ang isa ay maluwag♪

